    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056490/extras/f4345eeb7fd2e155eaa470a9627191bd.poster.avif?t=1749665193\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056490/extras/f4345eeb7fd2e155eaa470a9627191bd.webm?t=1749665193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056490/extras/f4345eeb7fd2e155eaa470a9627191bd.mp4?t=1749665193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>《陷阵孤雄》是一款带有roguelike和部分策略元素的回合制游戏。<br>英雄们没有退路，必须一往无前，在“被遗忘的原初世界”中冲锋陷阵，与成群的怪物战斗到底，以救赎自己的灵魂。 </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056490/extras/c28ffd2b83d6656551dfb17981878617.poster.avif?t=1749665193\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056490/extras/c28ffd2b83d6656551dfb17981878617.webm?t=1749665193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056490/extras/c28ffd2b83d6656551dfb17981878617.mp4?t=1749665193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏特色<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>六种使用独特战术的英雄<br><br></li><li>每位英雄都能使用独特的技能消灭亡灵。<br><br></li><li>休闲的回合制策略游戏，正确决策方能取胜。<br><br></li><li>正确规划前进路线：收集能增加英雄生存能力的物品，选择更好的路径以避免危险，并准备好面对“被遗忘的原初世界”的领主。<br><br></li><li>再来一局：如果你输了，再试一次——利用英雄的长处才能成功。你无法未雨绸缪，每一局都是新的开始。<br><br></li><li>没有退路！你不能后退，英雄可不能临阵脱逃！<br><br></li><li>支持键盘、鼠标或游戏手柄。</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2056490/extras/897af563b14e14fbcc85c9cbe4569b37.poster.avif?t=1749665193\" width=600 height=338 ><source src